     <div class="row patientheader">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-1">
       <h4>
        <a class="noshowlink" name="for_patients">
         <span class="lang_for_patients">
          For Patients
         </span>
        </a>
       </h4>
       <h2>
        <span class="lang_intl_patients">
         Advanced Medical Care that Speaks your Language
        </span>
       </h2>
      </div>
     </div>
     <div class="row patients">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-1 rule lang_intl_blurb">
       <p>
        Our International Programs team provides bilingual patient coordinators who will facilitate every aspect of your trip to Chicago and visit to the medical center. These dedicated coordinators will assist you in scheduling medical appointments, confirming treatment plans and obtaining any financial or insurance clearance needed. To meet your needs, we also have certified professional medical interpreters to provide translation services during appointments.
       </p>
       <p>
        To make traveling easier, we offer complimentary transportation to our international patients, providing transport to and from the airport and for all medical appointments. We will also assist you and your family in finding accommodations, whether you require hotel reservations or need to rent a furnished apartment for an extended stay. Our goal is to make your visit as comfortable and simple as possible.
       </p>
       <p class="download">
        <a '="" class="download_patient" href="#">
         Download Brochure
         <i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-o-down">
         </i>
        </a>
       </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 contactsidebar">
       <button class="downloadformcta lang_download_form">
