     <div class="row hospitalheader">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-1">
       <h4>
        <a class="noshowlink" name="for_hospitals">
         <span class="lang_for_hospitals">
          For Hospitals
         </span>
        </a>
       </h4>
       <h2>
        <span class="lang_intl_hospitals">
         Sharing our Expertise with Hospitals Around the World
        </span>
       </h2>
      </div>
     </div>
     <div class="row hospitals">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-1 rule lang_hospital_blurb">
       <p>
        The professional administrators and clinical personnel who work for the University of Chicago Medicine are available to share their knowledge and skill to support both new and existing hospital projects all over the world.
       </p>
       <p>
        Our experts are engaging their colleagues abroad in the following areas:
       </p>
       <ul>
        <li>
         International Accreditation
        </li>
        <li>
         Quality and Patient Safety
        </li>
        <li>
         Infection Control
        </li>
        <li>
         Operational Excellence and Lean Transformation
        </li>
        <li>
         Supply Chain Management
        </li>
        <li>
         Information Technology
        </li>
        <li>
         Strategic Planning and Marketing
        </li>
       </ul>
       <p>
        University of Chicago Medicine physicians, nurses and administrators who work in our international centers of excellence are also helping hospitals abroad to advance specific clinical specialties, such as:
       </p>
       <ul>
        <li>
         Radiology
        </li>
        <li>
         Pathology
        </li>
        <li>
         Stem Cell Transplantation
        </li>
        <li>
         Robotic Surgery
        </li>
        <li>
         Orthopaedic Surgery
        </li>
        <li>
         Cardiac and Thoracic Surgery
        </li>
        <li>
         Pancreatic Diseases and Interventional Endoscopy
        </li>
        <li>
         Urology
        </li>
        <li>
         Gynecology and Obstetrics
        </li>
        <li>
         Reconstructive Surgery, with a focus on Lymphedema Surgery
        </li>
        <li>
         Pain Management and Intensive Care
        </li>
       </ul>
       <p class="download">
